name: Alvinnn!!! and The Chipmunks
overview: Everyone's favorite chipmunks -- Alvin, Simon and Theodore -- are back in this computer-animated version of the classic animated series. The brothers are famous rock stars who tour around the world with their best friends, the Chipettes.

episodes.name: Alvin's Got A Brand New Bag
Dave Rebooted
episodes.overview: Dave gets temporary amnesia so the boys trick him into letting them skip school and go on a ski trip instead.

episodes.name: Germs
episodes.overview: Theodore becomes obsessed with cleanliness after a school speaker talks about the danger of germs.

episodes.name: A Rose by Any Other Name
Talking Teddy's Revenge
episodes.overview: Alvin thinks Theodore's teddy bear can tell the future, and goes all out to make Talking Teddy his friend.

episodes.name: Snail-A-Palooza
episodes.overview: Alvin lies to Theodore about a fake holiday to get out of chores, so Dave forces Alvin to make the holiday real.

episodes.name: Girls Night Out
episodes.overview: Dave discovers he's not too good at roughing it outdoors when he goes on a day hike with the Chipettes.

episodes.name: Tables Turned
episodes.overview: When Alvin pranks Simon with a trick website, the chipettes prank Alvin back.

episodes.name: Pizza Dash
episodes.overview: Simon creates a drone that can not only deliver pizzas, but has the ability to learn.

episodes.name: Glory Days
episodes.overview: Alvin worries that the munks are responsible for making Dave boring when they find out he used to be a rock star.

episodes.name: Switcheroo
episodes.overview: Theodore's teddy bear is bear-napped, forcing the boys to work with Officer Dangus to get him back.

episodes.name: The Paperboy
episodes.overview: Alvin starts stealing the morning paper to sell at school, but Dave blames the paperboy and refuses to pay up.

episodes.name: Britt's Picks
episodes.overview: Brittany's furious when she thinks Alvin has been writing on her blog and vows to get him back.

episodes.name: The Devil Wears Rodentia
episodes.overview: Brittany's dream of being a fashion designer turns into a nightmare when her ideas are stolen.

episodes.name: The C Team
episodes.overview: Coach Dobkins challenges Miss Smith and her ragtag team of outcasts to a baseball game to see who's the best.

episodes.name: The Toy
episodes.overview: A favorite toy of Theodore's is lost on a rafting trip but then mysteriously shows up at the house, and it's alive.

episodes.name: Theodore's Calling
episodes.overview: Miss Croner attempts to help Theodore discover his true calling in life.

episodes.name: Clumsy Jeanette
episodes.overview: Jeanette is suddenly the clumsiest person on the planet. Is there something wrong with her - or her new glasses?

episodes.name: Adventures in Babysitting
episodes.overview: Theodore gets roped into doing Alvin's babysitting sitting job with a spoiled four year old.

episodes.name: Alvin's Assistant
episodes.overview: Kevin agrees to be Alvin's assistant to get closer to the music industry, but ends up running errands instead.

episodes.name: Mysterions
episodes.overview: When Theodore discovers Alvin and Simon have a secret club, he promises not to tell anyone if they let him join.

episodes.name: The Crow That Ate My Homework
episodes.overview: Dave promises to take Alvin to a water park if he gets a good grade on his test, but then a crow steals it.

episodes.name: Alvin Management
episodes.overview: When Alvin accuses Dave of yelling at him too much, a therapist moves in to help Dave control his anger.

episodes.name: Time Capsule
episodes.overview: Alvin accuses Dave of yelling at him too much, so a therapist moves in;  when the school digs up an old high school time capsule, Miss Smith and Dave work together to keep an old secret.

episodes.name: Munk vs Machine
episodes.overview: The Chipmunks and Chipettes team up together to compete in a dodgeball tournament. They learned that an opposing team has an unfair advantage using technology. Later on, they discovered that an enraged Theodore could be their secret weapon.

episodes.name: Big Bro Theodore
episodes.overview: When Theodore mistakenly thinks he's the oldest brother, he tries to be a better role model for Alvin and Simon.

episodes.name: Granny Awards
episodes.overview: Dave is thrilled when he thinks he's nominated for a Grammy, but it's actually an award for aging musicians.

episodes.name: Artsy Smartsy
episodes.overview: Theodore helps Simon to try and get past his perfectionism in order to complete an art assignment for art class.

episodes.name: Between a Rope and a Hard Place
Taken
episodes.overview: The boy's imaginations run wild when Dave disappears. When they finally find him, they're convinced he's a zombie.
